      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THAT'S OUR GIRL (1) was fresh up last time at this track where she finished fourth (17.89) in a NG. Form at this distance is sound. The form out of her last race has been franked. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. QUEEN LOCH (2) goes very well over this track and trip including five wins. Recorded a neck win (16.08) in a Grade 5 last time at The Gardens. Looks one of the chances. PARK KEY PAW (8) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her solid 17.46 win at this track over 300m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Expecting another bold showing. FABIO ZED (3) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
